data.text:
Warrant Search

This page shows a list of persons with possibly active warrants held by law enforcement agencies in Black Hawk County, Iowa. If you know anyone who may be on the warrant list, you are encouraged to contact your local law enforcement agency or the Cedar Valley Crime Stoppers.

You should not attempt to physically apprehend any individual that may appear on this list and no action should be taken based solely on this listing. A warrant is an accusation of a criminal charge and all persons on this list are presumed innocent until proven guilty by a court of law.
